Recommends: hailo-tappas-core
Description: Hailo-8L Object Detection Streaming Service
 A headless object detection service that captures video from a USB camera,
 runs YOLOv8 inference on a Hailo-8L accelerator, and streams the annotated
 video via HTTP MJPEG.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time object detection using YOLOv8n on Hailo-8L (26 TOPS)
  - USB camera support via V4L2 (tested with DJI Osmo Pocket 3)
  - MJPEG streaming over HTTP for browser viewing
  - Web UI with real-time statistics
  - Headless operation optimized for Raspberry Pi CM5
